ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Technically demanding course but also an important component of an economics education
This course is very helpful if you are interested in doing research in labor economics because it gives exposure to many different topics and methodologies used in the current literature.
I would recommend the course to another student.
Yes. Broad coverage of relevant topics.

comments: Some of the more applied insights will be useful, particularly as they relate to empirical work
